# Admin Components And Media

Extract components according to ownership, not just first usage.

## Reusable Components

- Extract generic layout/chrome to `apps/admin/src/components/**`.
- Extract reusable data-owned components to the feature that owns the data:
  - Category selection UI belongs in `features/categories/components`.
  - Tax class selection UI belongs in `features/tax-classes/components`.
  - Media picking and assigned-media preview UI belongs in `features/media/components`.
- Product-specific orchestration remains in `features/products`, even when it composes shared media/category/tax components.

## Product Media Pattern

- `features/media` owns reusable media UI: picker modal, gallery/list/grid previews, upload selection UI.
- `features/products` owns product/variant media assignment: target shape, rank payload, update-product vs update-variant branching.
- Do not make media components depend on product IDs, variant IDs, or product DTOs.

## Product Variant Pattern

- Keep variant form mapping and labels in product utils/hooks.
- Reuse one variant details field component between default simple-product editing and variable-product drawer editing.
- Put product variant submit/update orchestration in hooks or the owning drawer/card, not in generic field components.
